                    <span>The Eye of the I is the book of all books. It spoke to my soul like no book/movie ever has. David Hawkins is a true avatar, and you can trust anything he has to say. This masterpiece has changed my view of life, and I will never be the same again- nor would I ever want to be. </span>
                  
